ContentDesc_Richtfeuer von Ridorana: South of Rabanastre, in a remote corner of the Valnard Sea gapes a fathomless maw that, for centuries, has slowly devoured the world around it: Ridorana. Whether you believe the cataract natural wonder or demon-torn gate to the very underworld, journeys to her edge should be made with the utmost caution, seeing as none who have stumbled into the darkness have ever returned to tell their tale. An ancient spire once used by the Dalmascans as a lighthouse rises defiantly above the churning waters to warn forethoughtful and foolhardy alike. It is into this spire that the transformed Ba'Gamnan has fled. It is into this hell that you must follow.
Instancecontenttextdata_19409_Text: Long has it been since I last gazed upon the open sky...and the vermin who scurry beneath her.
Instancecontenttextdata_19410_Text: With this vessel shall your doom be met.
Instancecontenttextdata_19411_Text: O darkest of vessels! You are my sword! You are my rain!
Instancecontenttextdata_19412_Text: O darkest of vessels! You are my bow! You are my rain!
Instancecontenttextdata_19413_Text: Behold as waters most foul spill forth to defile the land!
Instancecontenttextdata_19414_Text: Let the crashing waves cleanse you of your sins!
Instancecontenttextdata_19415_Text: Let the crashing waves bear you into the abyss!
Instancecontenttextdata_19416_Text: From brine are we born, unto brine shall we return.
Instancecontenttextdata_19417_Text: In darkness will you know true fear!
Instancecontenttextdata_19420_Text: INTRUDER ALERT! READYING VARIABLE WEAPONS SYSTEMS.
Instancecontenttextdata_19421_Text: ANOMALOUS INTELLIGENCE LEVELS DETECTED. REEDUCATION AUTHORIZED. BOOTING BASIC COMPUTATION PROTOCOL.
Instancecontenttextdata_19422_Text: BASIC COMPUTATION PROTOCOL LOADED. INITIATING LESSON.
Instancecontenttextdata_19423_Text: –-COMMAND–- ALIGN CURRENT VITALS WITH SPECIFIED MULTIPLES.
Instancecontenttextdata_19430_Text: REEDUCATION FAILED. SUBJECT DISMISSAL APPROVED. BOOTING TARTAREAN PROTOCOL.
Instancecontenttextdata_19431_Text: TARTAREAN PROTOCOL LOADED. INITIATING PROCESSING SEQUENCE COUNTDOWN.
Instancecontenttextdata_19432_Text: INITIATING PROCESSING SEQUENCE IN 25...24...23... SYSTEM ERROR!
Instancecontenttextdata_19433_Text: INITIATING PROCESSING SEQUENCE IN 3...2...1... PROCESSING SEQUENCE INITIATED.
Instancecontenttextdata_19434_Text: SUBJECT DISMISSAL FAILED. SUBJECT TERMINATION APPROVED. BOOTING ANNIHILATION MODE.
Instancecontenttextdata_19435_Text: WARNING! WARNING! RESEARCH STAFF: EVACUATE TO SHELTERS IMMEDIATELY!
Instancecontenttextdata_19437_Text: SYSTEM DAMAGE: 95%. ENTERING SAFE MODE... SYSTEMS OFFLINE...
Instancecontenttextdata_19438_Text: You will pay for what you have done...with blood!
Instancecontenttextdata_19439_Text: Scream louder! I want to remember this!
Instancecontenttextdata_19440_Text: Children of war, I am Belias. Come! Warm your hands at my fire!
Instancecontenttextdata_19444_Text: Bound by the march of time, forevermore!
Instancecontenttextdata_19446_Text: Rise, loyal minions. Heed my call!
Instancecontenttextdata_19447_Text: Step into the inferno! Step into my hellfire!
Instancecontenttextdata_19448_Text: Are you not yet ash and bone!?
Instancecontenttextdata_19451_Text: The Empire is a cancer, and I am the barber's blade!
Instancecontenttextdata_19452_Text: Feel the wrath of my brothers!
Instancecontenttextdata_19456_Text: We will discover Ba'Gamnan here within the lighthouse. I am certain of it.
Instancecontenttextdata_19457_Text: Did Ba'Gamnan─the Duma─give life to that creature!?
Instancecontenttextdata_19458_Text: The seal on the gate is lifted. We can now venture further up the lighthouse.
Instancecontenttextdata_19459_Text: This pattern... It is unmistakably─ No, it cannot be...
Instancecontenttextdata_19460_Text: The city remains functional...after all these centuries. Let us access the transportation nodes.
Instancecontenttextdata_19461_Text: The city's defenses also seem operational. Destroy them, if you must.
Instancecontenttextdata_19462_Text: The heat...is almost unbearable. Could this be the heart of the lighthouse's beacon?
Instancecontenttextdata_19464_Text: The architecture here is similar to that of the lighthouse...yet something feels off. The air...is so thin...
Instancecontenttextdata_19465_Text: I believe you've succeeded in clearing another path.
Instancecontenttextdata_19466_Text: Those golems... I believe I now know where we are!
Instancecontenttextdata_19467_Text: The area's final line of defense is upon us. We must proceed with the utmost caution!
Instancecontenttextdata_19468_Text: There is no mistaking it. We are in the legendary Clockwork City of Goug!
